OL,3,CQueen to give replacement Roo to
OL,4,Ccomplete US library's Winnie-the-Pooh
OL,5,Ctoy set
OL,7,FThe Queen will give a specially made
OL,8,Ftoy of Winnie-the-Pooh character Roo
OL,9,Fto the New York Public Library during
OL,10,Fthe state visit to the US to complete
OL,11,Fa set of the beloved characters in one
OL,12,Fof the institution's collections.
OL,14,FCamilla and the King are due to arrive
OL,15,Fin the US on Monday for a four-day
OL,16,Fvisit during which they will meet
OL,17,FDonald Trump and be guests of honour
OL,18,Fat a White House banquet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
