PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777169008
OL,3,CQueen to give replacement Roo to
OL,4,Ccomplete US library's Winnie-the-Pooh
OL,5,Ctoy set
OL,7,FThe Queen will give the library a Roo
OL,8,Fmade specifically for the visit by
OL,9,Ftraditional British teddy bear makers
OL,10,FMerrythought, who produced the
OL,11,Foriginal toys at the start of the 20th
OL,12,Fcentury.
OL,14,FThe design is based on the original
OL,15,Fillustrations.
OL,17,FThe Roo toy, currently in Buckingham
OL,18,FPalace, will join Camilla on the royal
OL,19,Fplane to make the transatlantic
OL,20,Fjourney.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/4
